    "In comparison to OASIS, the ADNI dataset used for this work lacks a sufficient number of representative cases for each stage across all possible scenarios.",
    "Table 5 compares the works that use MRI data as features for ML models.",
    "In some works, a hybrid dataset is used for training the ML models.",
